  "prompt": "Which is the best coaching in Patna for the IIT-JEE?",
  "response": "Choosing the best coaching institute for IIT-JEE preparation can be subjective and depends on various factors such as teaching methodology, faculty, past results, and student feedback. However, some of the well-known coaching institutes in Patna for IIT-JEE preparation include:\n\n1. **FIITJEE Patna**: Known for its structured and comprehensive study material, along with experienced faculty.\n\n2. **Allen Career Institute, Patna**: Popular for its rigorous training and consistent results. Allen has a good track record of students cracking the IIT-JEE.\n\n3. **Aakash Institute, Patna**: Offers integrated programs and has a strong reputation for preparing students for competitive exams like IIT-JEE.\n\n4. **Vibrant Academy, Patna**: Known for its focus on conceptual clarity and problem-solving skills.\n\n5. **Bansal Classes, Patna**: Has a good reputation for its teaching methodology and results in IIT-JEE.\n\nWhen selecting a coaching institute, consider visiting them, talking to current students or alumni, and assessing which one aligns best with your learning style and requirements. Also, it's important to complement coaching with self-study and practice to maximize your preparation for the IIT-JEE.",
